              <title>Track OER - status, 29 August: looking back, looking forward..</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6449</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6449</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>We prepared for the first round of testing, with LTS Technical Testing team at The Open University. This involved writing <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Hqqm1Rhmsi3SaWwMJ1mRE5gyyIdfFdxqM3D2LKxsYOc/edit">an initial test script</a>. And, significantly we relied on the <a href="http://capret.mitoeit.org">CaPReT evaluation server</a>, which does not have guaranteed up-time or support. So, we took a copy of the CaPReT Javascripts, and extended them to work with Piwik (capret-piwik.js).</p>
<p>Testing proceeded on schedule last week, and the <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ci8U920B6DgydrBZZvYZxtvOTw_OpH1AnCX61-OWjpA/edit">results are online</a>.</p>
