<p>Finally, I finished the command line batch processor. This is our initial solution to add license-tracker code into the HTML pages in the various Zip archives that can be downloaded from LabSpace. We are looking at XSLT solutions going forward, but this has enabled us to proceed with the <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RIWRsGFQf4CmiPoHl3BMubz3w6TMiFN_oQbnuSKtQA0/edit">second round of testing this week</a>.</p>
