                    <item>
              <title>Online OER Repository at the African Virtual University</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3823</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3823</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong><em>COMMING UP SOON</em></strong></p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->In line with the AVU Business Plan 2009-2014, the AVU is devloping of&nbsp;a new&nbsp;online OER Repository named <strong><a href="mailto:OER@AVU">OER@AVU</a>. It</strong>&nbsp;will serve as a platform to publish the 73 modules of&nbsp; Mathematics,&nbsp;Biology, Physics, Chemistry, Teacher Education professional courses, ICT Basic Skills and B.Ed. professional courses&nbsp;that were developed and released as OERs&nbsp;through a Multinational project involving 10 African countries. The modules were peer reviewed and are currently used in institutional programs in the 10 countries</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->The AVU OER&nbsp;Repository&nbsp;will also serve as a platform for tertiary-level African educators to make their educational resources available to others, discuss and comment on them, and collaborate in developing them further.</p>]]></description>
          <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jan 2011 22:51:00 +0000</pubDate>
