              <title>OER10: CORRE</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3159</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3159</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>Samuel Nikoi at Leicester University talked about an evaluation framework</p>]]></description>
