              <title>A. Programme</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2728</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2728</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS--><strong>A. Pre-virtual workshop</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p>
<ul style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->
list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;"&gt;
<li style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS--><a href="/index.php/cloud/view/2737">Welcome</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/cloud/view/2738">introductions</a> and <a href="/cloud/view/2740">ice-breaker</a></li>
<li style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Checklist: <a href="/cloud/view/2521">Introduction to Cloudworks: account and profile&nbsp;</a>and&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/cloud/view/2457">movie</a></li>
<li>Checklist: &nbsp;Tools&nbsp;quickstart guides&nbsp;- <a href="http://oufm.open.ac.uk/quickstart.html">FM</a>, <a href="http://www.elluminate.com/demo/recorded_demos_list.jsp">Elluminate</a> and <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GvA17aofzaM">Cohere</a> </li>
