                    <item>
              <title>How can we transfer good practice developed around one Open Educational Resource to inform the design of another?</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/1936</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/1936</guid>
